
Illustrates sharing variables and data between threads and also hints
as to the cost of some of the mutual exclusion constructs.

Run the programs using the time command and different numbers of
threads to explore speed.

sum ... original sequential sum code ... correct answer is N*(N-1)/2=49999995000000

atomic ... parallel sum using atomic

critical ... parallel sum using critical

reduction ... parallel sum using a reduction variable

mxm ... simple parallel matrix multiplication





